    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Map<K,​V>
    public final class LWWRegisterMap<K,​V>
extends java.util.AbstractMap<K,​V>
implements java.util.Map<K,​V>
    Convenience wrapper class for ORMap that uses LWWRegister's for values.

    This is useful as it allows the map to be used more idiomatically, with plain Map.get(Object) and Map.put(Object, Object) calls for values.
